Libraries used
* org.openkinect.*
* processing.opengl.*
* codeanticode.glgraphics.*
* deadpixel.keystone.* 
* Flocking 3D Birds by Ira Greenberg
* Kinect Tracking by Daniel Shiffmann
* Agents and Attractors from Generative Gestaltung book
